jsDoc.doc: The current release version of the intv8 warn package.
A class that collects warnings, logs them to a provided logger, and displays collected warnings.
Creates a new {@link WarningCollector} with the provided logger.
The warnings collected by this {@link WarningCollector}.
Adds a warning to the {@link WarningCollector}.
Migrate collected warnings to a new {@link WarningCollector}. Does not re-log warnings.
Returns warnings in the {@link WarningCollector}.
A warning alerting to future changes for a codebase.
Creates a new {@link FutureWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link FutureWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link FutureWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link FutureWarning} warning.
A warning alerting that a process may encounter issues. e.g. a dependency is not started and may cause issues, but will not prevent the process from starting.
Creates a new {@link ProcessWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link ProcessWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link ProcessWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link ProcessWarning} warning.
A warning alerting when an operation is expected to encounter memory issues.
Creates a new {@link MemoryWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link MemoryWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link MemoryWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link MemoryWarning} warning.
A warning alerting that a feature is pending deprecation.
Creates a new {@link DeprecationWarning} exception with the default message and no exception init properties.
Creates a new {@link DeprecationWarning} exception with a message created from the provided {@link DeprecationWarningInit} properties.
Creates a new {@link DeprecationWarning} exception with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link DeprecationWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link DeprecationWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link DeprecationWarning} warning.
A warning alerting that a feature is not stable, or has an indeterminant API, and should not be used in production.
Creates a new {@link StabilityWarning} exception with the default message and no exception init properties.
Creates a new {@link StabilityWarning} exception with a message created from the provided {@link StabilityWarningInit} properties.
Creates a new {@link StabilityWarning} exception with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link StabilityWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link StabilityWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link StabilityWarning} warning.
A warning alerting that a feature is pending deprecation.
Creates a new {@link PendingDeprecationWarning} exception with the default message and no exception init properties.
Creates a new {@link PendingDeprecationWarning} exception with a message created from the provided {@link PendingDeprecationWarningInit} properties.
Creates a new {@link PendingDeprecationWarning} exception with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link PendingDeprecationWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link PendingDeprecationWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link PendingDeprecationWarning} warning.
The base warning for OS-related warnings.
Creates a new {@link OSWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link OSWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link OSWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link OSWarning} warning.
A generic warning from which all warnings are derived.
Creates a new {@link Warning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link Warning} properties.
The warning code for the {@link Warning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link Warning} warning.
A warning alerting that an active connection may encounter issues. e.g. link quality, speed, etc.
Creates a new {@link ConnectionWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link ConnectionWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link ConnectionWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link ConnectionWarning} warning.
An warning alerting when an operation is expected to encounter disk issues.
Creates a new {@link DiskWarning} warning with the provided message, optionally with additional {@link DiskWarningInit} properties.
The warning code for the {@link DiskWarning} warning.
The warning init properties for the {@link DiskWarning} warning.
The global {@link WarningsManager} instance.
